   jsonb_build_array('Each additional hour of study is associated with a predicted increase of 4.5 points in quiz score.','A student who studies 0 hours is predicted to score 4.5 points.','Each additional point on the quiz is associated with 4.5 more hours of study.','The maximum possible quiz score is 62 plus 4.5 points.'),0,83,
   'The slope gives the predicted change in y (score) for each one-unit increase in x (hours).'),
